# Production build (used by `vite build`).
# Empty base => the client calls the API with relative paths (/api/v1/...),
# i.e. same-origin as the page. Behind the Cloudflare tunnel that single
# origin (https://mallardmanagement.tech) routes /api/* to the backend and
# everything else to this frontend, so no CORS and no hardcoded host:port.
VITE_GREENLIGHT_URL=
